[
    {
        "text": "Sometimes we need to complain.",
        "start": 0.16,
        "duration": 2.916
    },
    {
        "text": "But how can we do this politely",
        "start": 3.076,
        "duration": 3.004
    },
    {
        "text": "and in a British way?",
        "start": 6.08,
        "duration": 2.08
    },
    {
        "text": "First, we can begin 'would like to'",
        "start": 8.16,
        "duration": 3.04
    },
    {
        "text": "to say what we want.",
        "start": 11.2,
        "duration": 1.84
    },
    {
        "text": "'Hi i would like to speak to the manager.",
        "start": 13.04,
        "duration": 2.4
    },
    {
        "text": "Yes, I'd like to complain.'",
        "start": 15.44,
        "duration": 1.84
    },
    {
        "text": "We can say 'I am unhappy about'",
        "start": 17.28,
        "duration": 3.28
    },
    {
        "text": "plus a noun phrase.",
        "start": 20.56,
        "duration": 2.265
    },
    {
        "text": "'Yes, I am unhappy about my late delivery.'",
        "start": 22.825,
        "duration": 3.415
    },
    {
        "text": "We can also add 'very' or 'really'",
        "start": 26.24,
        "duration": 3.04
    },
    {
        "text": "to make this stronger.",
        "start": 29.28,
        "duration": 1.92
    },
    {
        "text": "'Yeah, I'm really unhappy about this.'",
        "start": 31.2,
        "duration": 2.88
    },
    {
        "text": "We can also say 'it's unacceptable that'",
        "start": 34.08,
        "duration": 3.36
    },
    {
        "text": "plus a clause.",
        "start": 37.44,
        "duration": 1.36
    },
    {
        "text": "'Yeah, it's unacceptableÂ \nthat my delivery is late.'",
        "start": 38.8,
        "duration": 4.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Remember, don't lose your temper.",
        "start": 42.8,
        "duration": 2.88
    },
    {
        "text": "This means 'don't become too angry' -",
        "start": 45.68,
        "duration": 3.44
    },
    {
        "text": "it's rude to lose your temper.",
        "start": 49.12,
        "duration": 2.4
    },
    {
        "text": "This is good advice -",
        "start": 51.52,
        "duration": 1.76
    },
    {
        "text": "we can say this to people who are angry with us:",
        "start": 53.28,
        "duration": 3.2
    },
    {
        "text": "'Alright! Don't lose your temper.'",
        "start": 56.48,
        "duration": 5.36
    }
]